title: OZZY OSBOURNE-Don't Blame Me(The Tales of Ozzy Osbourne)
description:
Don't Blame Me is a comprehensive documentary of rock superstar Ozzy Osbourne that explores in-depth his personal and professional life. Osbourne discusses information about his attempted suicide, his recovery from drug and alcohol abuse, his highly publicized stage antics, battling accusations he was a Satan worshiper, and a very personal look at his home life. This documentary includes music from his live-concert performances, such as "N.I.B.," "I Don't Know," "Mr. Crowley," "Mama, I'm Coming Home," and "War Pigs."
